    <p>Holy Grail is a front-end development toolkit targeted at being lightweight easy to use. It is built on <a href="http://bourbon.io/" target="_blank">Bourbon</a> and is heavily influenced by <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/" target="_blank">Bootstrap 3</a> and <a href="http://bitters.bourbon.io/" target="_blank">Bitters</a>. Holy Grail also includes tools such-as task-runners for asset compilation, a static site generator, and popular CMS boilerplate themes.</p>

