            <li><a href="{{ file.frontMatter.relative_nav_url }}features/wells.html">Wells &amp; Alerts</a></li>
            <li><a href="{{ file.frontMatter.relative_nav_url }}features/tables_extended.html">Tables</a></li>
          </ul>

        </div>

        <div class="col col_6 col_lg_12 pad_x_1">

          <h4>A Full Toolkit:</h4>

          <p>Pre-alpha versions of Holy Grail already sit side-by-side with some pretty cool pieces of software such-as:</p>

          <ul class="mar_clear_b">
            <li>Handlebars (as a Node.js-driven static site generator)</li>
            <li>Bootstrap 3 (stripped-down to it's layout and typographic libraries)</li>
            <li>WordPress/WooCommerce (as a starter-theme)</li>
            <li>Large enterprise applications to micro-apps &amp; websites</li>
            <li>Multiple proprietary publishing platforms</li>
          </ul>

